      • FoldableRoom

        public FoldableRoom​(int floor,
                    char block,
                    int number,
                    int capacity,
                    char letter)
        Five-argument constructor with the same exceptions as its superclass for the same instance variables, adding the letter 'a' or 'b' to the end of the room's identifier.
        Parameters:
        floor - the floor on which the room is.
        block - the block in which the room is.
        number - the number of the room.
        capacity - the capacity of the room.
        letter - the identifier for the different halves of the room.
